----- Original Message -----
From: Gayle Bechtel
To: Unschooling-dotcom@egroups.com
Sent: Tuesday, June 27, 2000 3:08 AM
Subject: Re: Fw: [Unschooling-dotcom] moving forward!!!

This is my third and maybe last.  I have been sick everytime I eat(yeah), also I have dizzy spells but Dr says these will pass with time.   I have 2 boys - 3 1/2 and 2(on the 7th of July).  I am hoping for a girl, especially since 3 boys under the age of 5 scares me.  I would probably go nuts - LOL. 
 
Gayle
----- Original Message -----
From: NumoAstro@...
To: Unschooling-dotcom@egroups.com
Sent: Monday, June 26, 2000 9:23 PM
Subject: Re: Fw: [Unschooling-dotcom] moving forward!!!

Congratulations on your upcoming new one... How many do you have?  What sexes
and ages?  How exciting to be starting on that journey again... I say rather
you than me as I had terrible morning sickness with Max and the thought of
going through 9 months of illness again is terrifying.  I had to be
hospitalized I was so ill and never thought I'd make it the whole way. 
Having said that I have 2 beautiful healthy boys that keep me tired and
excited all at once.

Hope this pregnancy is a smooth one.

Dawn F
